Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram showing the deployment process for the Stotra application:

```plantuml
@startuml spikecodes_stotra

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as CICD
participant "AWS Amplify" as Amplify
participant "AWS EC2" as EC2
participant "MongoDB Atlas" as MongoDB

Developer -> Git : Push code changes
Git -> CICD : Trigger build
CICD -> CICD : Run tests
CICD -> Amplify : Deploy frontend
Amplify -> Amplify : Build and host React app
CICD -> EC2 : Deploy backend
EC2 -> EC2 : Start Node.js server
EC2 -> MongoDB : Connect to database
Amplify --> Developer : Frontend deployed
EC2 --> Developer : Backend deployed

@enduml
```